thread.title_full: Redspot Car Rentals reviewed by VICTORIA

author: VICTORIA
title: VICTORIA
text: The amount I had to spend on the car almost doubled with the full insurance which was $35/day! (usually it's $7-$10). I went for it because it was the cheapest and I work for a not for profit and was surprised by the amount of the insurance which wasn't made clear when I booked
